local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["endanger"]={"endanger","[ɪn'deɪn(d)ʒə; en-]","[ɪn'dendʒɚ]","vt.危及",'vt.危及，危害','If we falter in our leadership, we may endanger the peace of the world, and we shall surely endanger the welfare of this nation.','如果我们的领导地位动摇了，不仅会危害世界的和平，而且一定会危害国家的安定。','He took over the post in the knowledge that it might endanger his life.','他在明知他的性命有可能受到威胁的情况下接任了那职位。'}
